\\n- Use Shadcn UI Navigation Menu\\n- Utilize Button components for social media links\\n- Implement Separator for visual division\\n\\n6. Responsiveness:\\n- Mobile: Collapse to single column\\n- Ensure touch-friendly icon sizes\\n- Maintain readability on smaller screens\\n\\n7. Interaction Notes:\\n- Smooth hover effects on links\\n- Subtle animations on social media icons\\n- Clickable logo that returns to home section\\n\\nThis plan provides a comprehensive, space-themed footer that maintains the inspirational and exploratory brand essence while offering clear navigation and contact options.\"}]}"
