            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-3-5-haiku-latest\",\"temperature\":0,\"top_k\":-1,\"top_p\":-1,\"stream\":false,\"max_tokens\":2048,\"tools\":[{\"name\":\"extract\",\"description\":\"A function available to call.\",\"input_schema\":{\"type\":\"object\",\"properties\":{\"availableSections\":{\"type\":\"array\",\"items\":{\"type\":\"string\"},\"description\":\"List of available sections for the Nav.\"},\"componentType\":{\"type\":\"string\",\"const\":\"Nav\"}},\"required\":[\"availableSections\",\"componentType\"],\"additionalProperties\":false,\"$schema\":\"http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#\"}}],\"tool_choice\":{\"type\":\"tool\",\"name\":\"extract\"},\"thinking\":{\"type\":\"disabled\"},\"messages\":[{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":\"Help the user plan a section of their website.\"},{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":\"I'll help plan the Navigation (Nav) section for the space exploration website. Based on the project summary, brand guidelines, and available sections, I'll create a comprehensive nav section plan.\\n\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"availableSections\\\": [\\n    \\\"Hero\\\",\\n    \\\"Features\\\", \\n    \\\"HowItWorks\\\", \\n    \\\"Testimonials\\\", \\n    \\\"CTA\\\"\\n  ]\\n}\\n```\\n\\nDetailed Section Plan for Navigation:\\n\\n1. Layout Description:\\n- Horizontal navigation bar spanning full width of page\\n- Centered logo on left side\\n- Navigation links aligned right\\n- Responsive mobile-friendly design with hamburger menu for smaller screens\\n\\n2. Visual Styling:\\n- Background: Deep space black (#0C0C1E)\\n- Text Color: Stellar white (#F0F4F8)\\n- Hover Effect: Soft blue glow (#3A7CA5) to evoke cosmic energy\\n- Typography: Clean, modern sans-serif (e.g., Inter or Roboto)\\n\\n3. Navigation Items:\\n- Logo: \\\"SpaceXplore\\\" with subtle star/galaxy icon\\n- Menu Links:\\n  1. Home (/#hero)\\n  2. Features (/#features)\\n  3. How It Works (/#howitworks)\\n  4. Testimonials (/#testimonials)\\n  5. Get Started (/#cta)\\n\\n4. Recommended Components:\\n- Use Shadcn UI's `navigation-menu.tsx`\\n- Use Shadcn UI's `button.tsx` for \\\"Get Started\\\" call-to-action\\n\\n5. Interactivity:\\n- Smooth scroll to section anchors\\n- Active link highlighting\\n- Subtle hover animations\\n\\n6. Responsiveness:\\n- Mobile: Collapse to hamburger menu using Shadcn UI's `sheet.tsx`\\n- Ensure touch-friendly sizing for mobile navigation\\n\\nThe navigation will create a seamless, space-themed user experience that guides visitors through the website's key sections while maintaining the inspirational and exploratory brand mood.\"}]}"
