            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-3-5-haiku-latest\",\"temperature\":0,\"top_k\":-1,\"top_p\":-1,\"stream\":false,\"max_tokens\":2048,\"tools\":[{\"name\":\"extract\",\"description\":\"A function available to call.\",\"input_schema\":{\"type\":\"object\",\"properties\":{\"suggestedComponents\":{\"anyOf\":[{\"type\":\"array\",\"items\":{\"type\":\"string\"}},{\"type\":\"null\"}],\"description\":\"List of suggested Shadcn UI components for this section.\"},\"headline\":{\"type\":[\"string\",\"null\"],\"description\":\"The headline for the CTA section (e.g., 'Ready to Get Started?').\"},\"supportingText\":{\"type\":[\"string\",\"null\"],\"description\":\"Supporting text for the CTA section (e.g., 'Don't miss out on this opportunity!').\"},\"paragraphs\":{\"type\":[\"string\",\"null\"],\"description\":\"Paragraphs of text to be included in the section.\"},\"cta\":{\"type\":\"object\",\"properties\":{\"text\":{\"type\":\"string\",\"description\":\"The text for the primary CTA button (e.g., 'Start Your Free Trial').\"}},\"required\":[\"text\"],\"additionalProperties\":false},\"supportingVisualOrTrustSignal\":{\"type\":[\"string\",\"null\"]},\"componentType\":{\"type\":\"string\",\"const\":\"CTA\"}},\"required\":[\"suggestedComponents\",\"headline\",\"supportingText\",\"paragraphs\",\"cta\",\"supportingVisualOrTrustSignal\",\"componentType\"],\"additionalProperties\":false,\"$schema\":\"http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#\"}}],\"tool_choice\":{\"type\":\"tool\",\"name\":\"extract\"},\"thinking\":{\"type\":\"disabled\"},\"messages\":[{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":\"Help the user plan a section of their website.\"},{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":\"I'll help plan the CTA (Call-to-Action) section for the space exploration website based on the provided context. I'll generate a comprehensive section plan that captures the inspirational and awe-inspiring tone of space exploration.\\n\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"suggestedComponents\\\": [\\n    \\\"@/components/ui/button.tsx\\\",\\n    \\\"@/components/ui/card.tsx\\\"\\n  ],\\n  \\\"headline\\\": \\\"Begin Your Space Journey Today\\\",\\n  \\\"supportingText\\\": \\\"Space tourism slots for 2024 are filling rapidly. Don't miss your chance to be among the first civilian explorers of the final frontier.\\\",\\n  \\\"paragraphs\\\": null,\\n  \\\"cta\\\": {\\n    \\\"text\\\": \\\"Secure Your Cosmic Ticket\\\"\\n  },\\n  \\\"supportingVisualOrTrustSignal\\\": \\\"A subtle starry background or a small icon of a rocket to reinforce the space exploration theme\\\"\\n}\\n```\\n\\nLet me break down the detailed plan for this CTA section:\\n\\n🎯 Section Goal:\\nThe primary objective is to create a compelling final push that motivates users to take immediate action and sign up for space tourism.\\n\\n📝 Content Strategy:\\n- Headline: \\\"Begin Your Space Journey Today\\\" - Direct, action-oriented, and inspiring\\n- Supporting Text: Emphasizes scarcity and uniqueness of the opportunity\\n- CTA Button: \\\"Secure Your Cosmic Ticket\\\" - Playful, specific, and exciting\\n\\n🎨 Visual Design Considerations:\\n- Use a deep, rich black background reminiscent of space\\n- Incorporate subtle stellar particle effects or gradient backgrounds\\n- Ensure high contrast between text and background for readability\\n- Use modern, clean typography that \\\"floats\\\" like objects in space\\n\\n📱 Responsiveness:\\n- On mobile, stack elements vertically\\n- Ensure CTA button is large and easily tappable\\n- Maintain spacious margins to prevent a cluttered look\\n\\n🧩 Recommended Components:\\n- Shadcn Button for the primary CTA\\n- Card component to create a contained, focused area\\n- Potential use of Tooltip for additional information\\n\\nThe section is designed to be the final, compelling argument that transforms interested visitors into active participants in the space tourism program.\"}]}"
