            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-3-5-haiku-latest\",\"temperature\":0,\"top_k\":-1,\"top_p\":-1,\"stream\":false,\"max_tokens\":2048,\"tools\":[{\"name\":\"extract\",\"description\":\"A function available to call.\",\"input_schema\":{\"type\":\"object\",\"properties\":{\"suggestedComponents\":{\"anyOf\":[{\"type\":\"array\",\"items\":{\"type\":\"string\"}},{\"type\":\"null\"}],\"description\":\"List of suggested Shadcn UI components for this section.\"},\"headline\":{\"type\":[\"string\",\"null\"],\"description\":\"The headline for the features section (e.g., 'Explore Key Features').\"},\"subheadline\":{\"type\":[\"string\",\"null\"],\"description\":\"Supporting text below the headline.\"},\"paragraphs\":{\"type\":[\"string\",\"null\"],\"description\":\"Paragraphs of text to be included in the section.\"},\"features\":{\"type\":\"array\",\"items\":{\"type\":\"object\",\"properties\":{\"name\":{\"type\":\"string\",\"description\":\"The name of the feature.\"},\"description\":{\"type\":\"string\",\"description\":\"A brief description of the feature.\"},\"visual\":{\"type\":[\"string\",\"null\"],\"description\":\"Description of the desired primary visual (image/video).\"}},\"required\":[\"name\",\"description\",\"visual\"],\"additionalProperties\":false}},\"cta\":{\"type\":[\"string\",\"null\"],\"description\":\"Text for a call-to-action button, if desired.\"},\"componentType\":{\"type\":\"string\",\"const\":\"Features\"}},\"required\":[\"suggestedComponents\",\"headline\",\"subheadline\",\"paragraphs\",\"features\",\"cta\",\"componentType\"],\"additionalProperties\":false,\"$schema\":\"http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#\"}}],\"tool_choice\":{\"type\":\"tool\",\"name\":\"extract\"},\"thinking\":{\"type\":\"disabled\"},\"messages\":[{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":\"Help the user plan a section of their website.\"},{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":\"I'll help plan the Features section for the space exploration landing page, focusing on creating an inspiring and informative overview of space exploration capabilities.\\n\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"suggestedComponents\\\": [\\n    \\\"@/components/ui/card.tsx\\\",\\n    \\\"@/components/ui/icons/telescope.tsx\\\",\\n    \\\"@/components/ui/icons/rocket.tsx\\\"\\n  ],\\n  \\\"headline\\\": \\\"Exploring the Cosmic Frontier\\\",\\n  \\\"subheadline\\\": \\\"Transforming Humanity's Greatest Adventure into Tangible Progress\\\",\\n  \\\"paragraphs\\\": \\\"Space exploration represents more than technological achievement—it's a testament to human curiosity, innovation, and our collective potential to transcend known boundaries. Each mission expands our understanding of the universe and our place within it.\\\",\\n  \\\"features\\\": [\\n    {\\n      \\\"name\\\": \\\"Advanced Spacecraft Technology\\\",\\n      \\\"description\\\": \\\"Cutting-edge propulsion systems and materials that enable longer, safer journeys into deep space, pushing the boundaries of human exploration beyond previous limitations.\\\",\\n      \\\"visual\\\": \\\"rocket icon from lucide-react\\\"\\n    },\\n    {\\n      \\\"name\\\": \\\"Satellite Observation Networks\\\",\\n      \\\"description\\\": \\\"Comprehensive global and interplanetary monitoring systems that provide unprecedented insights into planetary dynamics, climate patterns, and cosmic phenomena.\\\",\\n      \\\"visual\\\": \\\"telescope icon from lucide-react\\\"\\n    },\\n    {\\n      \\\"name\\\": \\\"Interplanetary Research Platforms\\\",\\n      \\\"description\\\": \\\"Modular research stations designed to support extended missions, enabling scientific teams to conduct groundbreaking experiments in microgravity and extreme environments.\\\",\\n      \\\"visual\\\": \\\"satellite icon from lucide-react\\\"\\n    }\\n  ],\\n  \\\"cta\\\": \\\"Join the Cosmic Journey\\\"\\n}\\n```\\n\\nThis plan captures the essence of space exploration by:\\n1. Using an inspiring headline that speaks to human potential\\n2. Providing a compelling subheadline that frames space exploration as a transformative endeavor\\n3. Creating feature descriptions that highlight technological capabilities\\n4. Suggesting appropriate Shadcn UI components for implementation\\n5. Including a motivational call-to-action\\n\\nThe section aims to evoke wonder while presenting concrete capabilities, aligning perfectly with the brand's inspirational and awe-inspiring tone.\\n\\nWould you like me to elaborate on any aspect of this section plan?\"}]}"
