            "text": "{\"id\":\"msg_01WrNqUVtn5gKraspKU4VnSd\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"model\":\"claude-3-5-haiku-20241022\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"id\":\"toolu_01Xz4ytj7PX3EFAjFgXodvPv\",\"name\":\"extract\",\"input\":{\"suggestedComponents\":[\"@/components/ui/card.tsx\",\"@/components/ui/button.tsx\"],\"headline\":\"Your Journey to the Stars Begins Here\",\"subheadline\":\"Discover how our space exploration program transforms cosmic dreams into reality\",\"paragraphs\":\"Our comprehensive space exploration program connects you directly with the cutting edge of human achievement. From virtual mission control experiences to actual space tourism opportunities, we're making space accessible to dreamers and pioneers like you.\",\"steps\":[{\"title\":\"Explore Your Mission\",\"description\":\"Browse our curated selection of space experiences, from immersive virtual simulations to potential real-world space tourism opportunities. Each mission is designed to inspire and educate.\",\"visual\":\"Telescope icon from Lucide React representing exploration and discovery\"},{\"title\":\"Select Your Adventure\",\"description\":\"Choose from our range of programs - whether you're a space enthusiast looking for a virtual experience or an aspiring astronaut seeking real-world training and potential space travel.\",\"visual\":\"Rocket icon from Lucide React symbolizing space travel and adventure\"},{\"title\":\"Prepare and Launch\",\"description\":\"Engage with our comprehensive training modules, connect with space experts, and prepare for an extraordinary journey that pushes the boundaries of human experience.\",\"visual\":\"Launch icon from Lucide React representing preparation and takeoff\"},{\"title\":\"Expand Your Cosmic Perspective\",\"description\":\"Join a community of explorers, share your experiences, and become part of humanity's ongoing mission to understand and explore the vast universe around us.\",\"visual\":\"Globe icon from Lucide